t names: **Garage Discovery**, **Foundry Pilot**, **Factory Enterprise Rollout**, and **Operate Managed AI Operations**.\n\n#### 4. Interaction Strategy\n- Hover micro-interactions on every dimension card and node card, shifting borders and adding a subtle sapphire glow to reflect advanced platform states.\n- Responsive, expensive entrance animations utilizing simple CSS transitions or Tailwind animation states.\n\n#### 5. Mobile Strategy\n- Fully responsive stacked cards on smaller screen dimensions.\n- Responsive 2-column or 1-column layouts for the bento grids.\n- Flexible text wrapping and legible sizing of SVGs.\n\n#### 6. Files to Change\n- `/lib/blueprint-data.ts`: Implement exact dimension breakdown scores, formulas, and test-case consistency logic.\n- `/components/sections/BlueprintGenerator.tsx`: Incorporate premium Dimension Breakdown bento grid, CSS/SVG charts, updated 4-phase 90-day roadmap names, and refined mobile-ready layouts.\n\n#### 7. Files Not to Touch\n- Any landing page files (`app/page.tsx` or similar), ensuring strict compliance with `allowLandingChanges: false`.\n- Do not reintroduce any slug or PublicRoutePage components.\n\n---\n\nLet's edit `lib/blueprint-data.ts` first. I will replace the existing `calculateBlueprintScore` logic and add `calculateBlueprintDimensions`. Let's make sure the file is written correctly. I will use the `editor` tool."}}
